{
  "stem": "10181.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I remember the-- the orphanage much better than I remember the school, OK, because it sort of, I guess, left more of an impression on me, being organized.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- and-- and it was, you know, [? even ?] [? nice ?] to go to [? there ?] [? now. ?] Also, all the-- now that I remember, when I think about it, the Jewish holidays.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You asked me before about the Jewish holidays.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We used to go there, actually, now that I think about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I remember having one Purim there, and they had a play, you know, on the stage where the older-- older orphanage people, the members, performed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was very good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And-- and Passover-- and I remember now, come to think of it, that's where we used to go because I don't-- I didn't remember anything in the house, really, but I do remember going to the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And that's-- that's where we all-- everybody went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Everybody went there later on, you know, because that was like the central place, you know, for everybody to get together.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And it was a fairly sizable place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There probably were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I-- I remember something, but I don't really remember, you know, because it went sort of by me, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was adults talking to each other, and-- and they sort of try to shield you from that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I don't really know-- I know that some of the older-- older boys-- the orphanage was to about, I think, age 16 or 17 or 18.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know because, really-- the-- I'll tell you who tried to explain to me, strangely enough.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The people upstairs were not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was of a retired policeman, and his wife, they were grandparent, but they-- the children [? can't ?] live somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I used to go there a lot, also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because he used to tell me stories about the First World War, which I don't know why I found it interesting, but I guess I found it interesting.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he tried to explain to me what was happening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, because you're Jewish, you know, you have these problems.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he didn't really explain it that well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I guess, he didn't think that a child of my age would understand it anyway.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he tried to explain that it wasn't-- he didn't feel that it was right.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, it was wrong.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was against this type of demonstrations and-- and beatings and whatever-- what was happening.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Don't forget, it was a small town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody knew-- knew everybody, so they were careful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Usually, they were out-- they brought in outsiders.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Nazis brought outsiders to do the bad things because the-- many years, everybody had lived together and worked together.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And everybody knew my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Even so he had died in the meanwhile, but they all knew my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My grandfather used to play cards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was a card player.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, and the German-- there's a Germany card game called skat, which I don't know how it goes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I have no-- I don't have a clue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I know my uncle used to play down-- even when I-- when I saw him years later, and he used to play, and he was well-known for that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He used to play a lot of friends, and-- and the whole town knew him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they knew my father well because he had served in-- in the First World War, and they had a lot of friends.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And-- but then, slowly but surely, I guess some of them started to distance themselves.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I don't think the-- the town-- the people that lived there for a while in the town, [? well, ?] they were not active in-- in-- in any of the early incidents, at least.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I know that, later on, it got worse, you know, but at the beginning, I guess, friendship from way past still meant something.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Even ?] I remember that when-- one day when I went for a walk with my grandfather, some so-called friends of his were no better.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They started calling-- calling him dirty Jew and-- and-- and all this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And these were people who we had known for many years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was frightened, you know, because, I think, my grandfather was in shock.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he didn't-- of all people, didn't expect it from them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he-- we were sitting on a bench, so we got up and we left and went back home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in general, you know, when you're-- I was four or five years old.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
